# Cart & Checkout UX

- Instant feedback on line edits; no heavy GSAP timelines
- Disable double-submit on pay
- Preserve form state on recoverable errors
- Server recomputes totals — never trust client money
- Show shipping/tax clearly when known; no surprise jumps late
- Guest checkout allowed per PRD; deterministic login merge
- Loading skeletons > opaque spinners that hide errors
- Success page: reassurance + order id + next steps

Security and idempotency beat animation polish on this path.
